*"Mi smo zajedno* (We are together).
*"Ona je išla zajedno* sa njim (She went with him).
*"Oni rade zajedno* svaki dan (They work together every day).
*"Oni su se družili zajedno* (They were hanging out together).
*"Oni su se smejali zajedno* (They were laughing together).
*"Oni su putovali zajedno* (They were travelling together).
*"Oni su stvorili zajedno* nešto lepo (They created something beautiful together).
*"Oni su se zajedno* smuvali (They flirted together).